<h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  " id="details-title">Details</h2>


<div aria-labelledby="details-title">
  
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<div class="call-to-action">
<h2 id="stay-up-to-date">Stay up to date</h2>

<p>The UK is leaving the EU. This page tells you how to prepare for Brexit and will be updated if anything changes.</p>

<p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/email-signup?topic=%2Fbrexit" class="govuk-link">Sign up for email alerts</a> to get the latest information.</p>
</div>

<p>This guidance explains how to obtain a Written Confirmation for each shipment of Active Substances manufactured in the UK that is exported to the EEA.</p>

<p>In a no-deal Brexit, we will continue to accept importation of active substances into the UK without a Written Confirmation from the same list of countries as currently (European Economic Area (EEA) countries, USA, Japan, Brazil, Australia, Israel and Switzerland).</p>

<p>Further guidance is available on <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/list-of-approved-countries-for-authorised-human-medicines-in-a-no-deal-scenario" class="govuk-link">importation of active substances from countries on a list</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>

</div>

